    "Conversely, a larger t value leads to extended reasoning times.",
    "In practice, we set t = 25 to achieve the best performance in all experiments.",
    "A.7 Validation on Enhanced Text PromptThere are various methods exist for video captioning annotation.",
    "For example, 360DVD [65] employs BLIP [85], which is tailored for captioning tasks, while LanguageBind [67] uses the multimodal large model OFA [86].",
    "However, we observe that both specialized and general models have limitations in comprehending metamorphic videos."
